Package: PeakRankR
Title: Rank Enhancer Peaks for Cloning
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Allen Institute", role = c("aut", "cph")),
    person("Saroja", "Somasundaram", role = "aut"),
    person("Nelson", "Johansen", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "nelsonj@alleninstitute.org")
  )
Description: Prioritizes a list of enhancer peaks from different cell groups
    (e.g., cell types, subclasses) for experimental cloning and targeting.
    Given a TSV file with genomic coordinates, group labels, and signal
    magnitude, along with a table of bigwig file paths, the package scores
    each peak on specificity, sensitivity, and magnitude, then returns a
    ranked list per group.
